OL,6,FIn 2020, Smajo founded the . He was
OL,7,Frecently also honoured with an OBE for
OL,8,Fservices to genocide education and
OL,9,Fcommemoration in the 2023 New Year
OL,10,FHonours list.
OL,12,FSmajo was just seven years old when
OL,13,Fthe war broke out in Bosnia. His
OL,14,Ffather and several male relatives were
OL,15,Ftortured in concentration camps, as
OL,16,FBosnian Muslims became targets of
OL,17,Fgenocide.
OL,19,FMr Beso said: "The Bosnian Genocide
OL,20,Fhappened in the heart of Europe just
OL,21,F50 years on from the Holocaust.
