OL,6,F"The lesson from Bosnia is that we
OL,7,Fmust never be complacent or take peace
OL,8,Ffor granted because it exposed how
OL,9,Fvulnerable and fragile society can be.
OL,11,F"Learning from the Holocaust, and
OL,12,Fsubsequent genocides like the one in
OL,13,FBosnia, can enhance our understanding
OL,14,Fof possible warning signs or patterns
OL,15,Fand, most importantly, it can better
OL,16,Fequip us to actively work towards
OL,17,Fpreventing future atrocities.
